data.meta_description: Join us weekly for our treadmill interval workouts, HIIT and strength classes. We also provide access to our Woodway treadmills and strength equipment during our Open Gym/Tread hours for individuals to complete their own workouts. Our gym is  conveniently located off of Forest Ave in Portland Maine.

data.text: Sign up to be the first to find out about our events, promotions, challenges, and more! We provide you with bi-monthly training advice to keep you training healthy year round! We respect your privacy and will never share your information with any third-party vendors.
